  - npcData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 843bf28d5b3e1234f9f70d090a25352d, type: 2}
    sentence: <speed=30>First equip the hoe by clicking it inside your inventory.
      Then it will show up on your tools bar just on top of the screen.
  - npcData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 843bf28d5b3e1234f9f70d090a25352d, type: 2}
    sentence: '<speed=30>In the farm area, surrounded by fences you can click <b>1</b>
      to use the hoe and plow the ground.

      Remember, you can only plant seed
      once the ground is prepared.'
  - npcData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 6fcb38fd7a4c9fe44a04ddf95729c090, type: 2}
    sentence: <speed=30>Thanks dad! This is a nice hoe, can't believe it's my first
      hoe!
  - npcData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 843bf28d5b3e1234f9f70d090a25352d, type: 2}
    sentence: <speed=30>You're welcome son, talk to me again when you are ready to
